description:
The easiest way to use MegaLights in Unreal Engine 5 https://youtu.be/A_7t9BqeQ_A

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This tutorial is for mid to advanced level however, I tried to keep things as simple as I could. We went through multiple topics starting from project download, project settings, setting up ambient lighting, and choosing the proper sky. And then we started breaking down the lights used and then using the additional fog layers to improve the scene depth.
